_sText: Yeah theres the main room and then 2 rooms next to that, then you teleport to a jump room and then do a jump bit, small bits of stuff to get you over a bit that takes you back to the start .... then theres a laser room - u die if you touch them .... then the final room has a mass teleporter which teleports everyone left in all the other rooms and freezes them in mid air so you can pwnzerize them....... above a blocky thing
